    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/c2219902c246f0177b1dc1789f5bee2f.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/c2219902c246f0177b1dc1789f5bee2f.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/174a0980c0c9d954990c1113f15ac0e0.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>团队合作至关重要。在《夺蛋奇兵》中，您和您的团队必须依靠策略、分散注意力和快速反应来战胜怪物并生存下来。每一个决定都很重要，因为一个失误就可能让整个团队付出代价。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/21cb338952ee6303ec62a821246d2eca.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/21cb338952ee6303ec62a821246d2eca.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/ed082111da7521b52aa3f9435d560ceb.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/ed082111da7521b52aa3f9435d560ceb.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/ed082111da7521b52aa3f9435d560ceb.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《彩蛋奇兵》中的怪物并不只是无脑的生物，它们受本能驱使，要保护自己的领地不受入侵者侵犯。一旦它们发现了你，就会不惜一切代价追踪你。您的团队必须保持警惕，利用一切可以利用的工具躲避它们的穷追不舍。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/3cea6cd0ba10dac702b948817995784a.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/3cea6cd0ba10dac702b948817995784a.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/86c8f9ad73fa517a73fc2e3708abb13f.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/86c8f9ad73fa517a73fc2e3708abb13f.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/86c8f9ad73fa517a73fc2e3708abb13f.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>时间就是生命。您在游戏中只有三天时间来掠夺、生存并尽可能多地赚钱。时间在一分一秒地流逝，每一个决定--是延长逗留时间以获得更多战利品，还是安全逃离--都会影响您的进度。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/2d0d0b637b531390901591b96c055f11.avif?t=1731476530\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras_big/2d0d0b637b531390901591b96c055f11.avif?t=1731476530 width=800 height=100 /></span></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/548578ba608bcf2ca8004b874a21b870.poster.avif?t=1731476530\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/548578ba608bcf2ca8004b874a21b870.webm?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253440/extras/548578ba608bcf2ca8004b874a21b870.mp4?t=1731476530\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>是留下来再抢一次，抢到有价值的物品，还是现在就带着自己的东西逃走？冒险越深入，逗留时间越长，收获就越大，但风险也越大。贪婪可能带来财富，也可能给你带来灭顶之灾。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
